Assignment 4 – XPath Basics 

Website: https://www.flipkart.com/ 

Tasks: 

- Close login popup using XPath with text(). 
//text
A--> driver.findElement(By.xpath("//button[text()='✕']")).click();

- Search for 'Mobiles' using XPath with contains(). 
A--> driver.findElement(By.xpath("//input[contains(@title, "Search for")]")).sendKeys("mobile");

- Apply filter (e.g., “4★ & above”) using XPath axes (following-sibling). 
A--> WebElement element= driver.findElement(By.xpath("//div[text()='Customer Ratings']"));
		JavascriptExecutor js = (JavascriptExecutor) driver;
		js.executeScript("window.scrollBy(0, 1000);");

        // Click "Custpmer Rating" element using JS
        js.executeScript("arguments[0].click();", element);
		//Click "4★ & above" rating option from the list.
		driver.findElement(By.xpath("//div[text()='4★ & above']/preceding-sibling::div")).click();

